title: NetObjects Fusion 11
description:
NetObjects Fusion 11


An intuitive website design program that creates a       
true drag-and-drop experience for both designers and    
developers. Quickly layout images, text or any object   
exactly where you want it on the page. Easily create     
professional Ajax user interfaces with the power of      
XHTML, CSS, JavaScript and XML. Data-bind any object    
to database or RSS feeds to add dynamic content to your site.                                                     
All this can be achieved without typing one line of code.                     
 


 Key new features in Fusion 11:                           
                                                          
 -Ajax UI Components                                     
 -Ajax Effects and Transitions                           
 -Data-source XML Binding                                  
 -Data-bind to any object                                 
 -XHTML 1.0 Publishing                                   
 -Automatic Code Hinting                                 
 -Integrate custom scripts                                
 -Image Gallery                                           
 -Google Site Traffic Tools                              
 -Built-in Flash Web Apps
